{
  "stem": "3040.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we work with Yad Vashem, contribute occasionally to the publications that Yad Vachem has.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And their publication is And the publication of Benjamin Meed is called Besides that, though I am quite busy publishing our own newsletter, which I will want to show you at least the cover of it, of our last issue.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it gives me a lot of satisfaction, and it gives me something to do in my retirement.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this is a standard question that every survivor hears at one time or another.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I was very religious and believing individual, I would say there was a purpose.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I survived with a mission, to carry on the memory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I mean, this is a point of view.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I-- I am not a hypocrite.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And to say that I survived so that I can carry the message is a little-- to-- to me, it's far-fetched.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It doesn't mean that it doesn't-- it doesn't put an obligation on me to do just that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This is the reason that I am doing this interview, that people, other people, can learn from it, and-- and-- and the people who try to deny it will be refuted by this-- by this-- by my testimony.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But if you asked me why I think I survived, only God knows.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was lots of luck, lots of luck, and lots of luck.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have dreams.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I always had dreams.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're not-- maybe not as frequent as some other people's.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some-- there are people who really suffer from these dreams almost every night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't get them every night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But occasionally, but occasionally, I get things-- to see things that I forgot completely that they happened.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, they come alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
